resources.string:
In the remote device

Start the application 'Remote Android';

Select 'Expose the device';

Select 'QRCode';

Present the QRCode;
 Then, scan the QRCode to initiate the connection between devices.

In the remote device

Start the application 'Remote Android';

Select 'Expose the device';

Select 'SMS';

Select the phone number of the current device;

Send an SMS;
 Then, wait to receive this message.

In the remote device

Start the application 'Remote Android';

Select 'Expose the device';

Select 'Input';
 Then, enter the displayed code and validate to initiate a connection.
